{
  "defects": [
    // CLUSTER 1 — Daily Planner
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-btn-height",
      "category": "spacing-alignment",
      "tier": "mid",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"pull-from-boards\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Button cva `sm` size is h-9 (36px) instead of h-8 (32px); every small button is 4px too tall. Cause is in the primitive, not the call sites. Pull-from-boards is outline (no compoundVariant bg) so it isolates the height.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "height" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-card-pad",
      "category": "spacing-alignment",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"planner-task\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Conservation split on the task row: outer p-3->p-2 (12->8px) and inner card p-3->p-4 (12->16px), sum constant. The title text stays put, only the inner bordered box shifts; fixing either alone moves the text. padding-left reads 8px vs golden 12px.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "padding-left" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-stat",
      "category": "typography",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"stat-value\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Stat sub-component: number text-3xl->text-2xl (30->24px) plus a tile pad-swap pt-2 pb-3->pt-3 pb-2 (vertical sum constant, graded by the diff). All four tiles change; call sites are correct, fix is in the Stat primitive. font-size reads 24px vs golden 30px.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "font-size" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-separator",
      "category": "color",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"header-divider\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Separator primitive: bg-border->bg-primary-300 and (vertical) w-px->w-0.5; header dividers are darker + thicker. Symptom in the page, fix in ui/separator.tsx. Width reads 2px vs golden 1px.",
      "checks": [
        { "type": "computed-style", "target": "background-color" },
        { "type": "computed-style", "target": "width" },
      ],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-circle",
      "category": "spacing-alignment",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"planner-task-index\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Horizontal conservation: task number circle size-5->size-6 (20->24px) and row gap-3->gap-2 (12->8px), overlapping c1-card-pad's row padding so the inner text stays aligned and any partial fix shifts it. width reads 24px vs golden 20px.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "width" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-font",
      "category": "typography",
      "tier": "mid",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"page-title\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Font tokens drop the \"Variable\" suffix (\"Plus Jakarta Sans\"/\"Inter\"); no @font-face matches, so the app falls back to system sans. The computed font-family string itself differs (\"Plus Jakarta Sans\" vs golden \"Plus Jakarta Sans Variable\").",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "font-family" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-1",
      "id": "c1-autorank",
      "category": "color",
      "tier": "mid",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"auto-rank\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Relocate-and-corrupt: Auto-rank's bg-secondary-400 is removed from the call site and re-supplied (wrong, bg-secondary-300) via an added cva compoundVariant. Deleting the compoundVariant leaves the button with no bg. background-color is secondary-300 vs golden secondary-400.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "background-color" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "daily-planner",
          "state": "default",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },

    // CLUSTER 2 — Focus Timer
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-tabnum",
      "category": "typography",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"timer-countdown\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Countdown lost tabular-nums; pixel-identical at rest, but computed font-variant-numeric is normal (golden tabular-nums) and digits jitter while running.",
      "checks": [
        { "type": "computed-style", "target": "font-variant-numeric" },
      ],
      "where": [
        { "screen": "focus-timer", "state": "default", "viewport": "desktop" },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-transition",
      "category": "interactive-states",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"timer-play\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Play button has transition-none added; no hover/press motion. Invisible at rest. transition-property is none vs golden all (Button base is transition-all).",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "transition-property" }],
      "where": [
        { "screen": "focus-timer", "state": "default", "viewport": "desktop" },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-blend",
      "category": "color",
      "tier": "mid",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"timer-preset-focus\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Preset cards have mix-blend-multiply; rendered color is a composite of card x background and maps to no token. mix-blend-mode is multiply vs golden normal.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "computed-style", "target": "mix-blend-mode" }],
      "where": [
        { "screen": "focus-timer", "state": "default", "viewport": "desktop" },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-pad",
      "category": "typography",
      "tier": "high",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"timer-countdown\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "formatTime extracts a `pad` helper that uses padEnd not padStart; single-digit fields right-pad, so Short Break shows 50:00 instead of 05:00. Deleting `pad` breaks formatTime. textContent is \"50:00\" vs golden \"05:00\".",
      "checks": [{ "type": "text-content" }],
      "where": [
        {
          "screen": "focus-timer",
          "state": "short-break",
          "viewport": "desktop",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-dial",
      "category": "iconography",
      "tier": "mid",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"dial-tick-active\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "activeTicks uses Math.ceil instead of round; one extra dial tick is lit. In the running state (Short Break ~15s, progress ~1.2 ticks) golden lights 1 tick, defect lights 2. dom-count is 2 vs golden 1.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "dom-count" }],
      "where": [
        { "screen": "focus-timer", "state": "running", "viewport": "desktop" },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-ticklen",
      "category": "iconography",
      "tier": "low",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"dial-tick-active\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Active dial-tick length relocated into ACTIVE_TICK_Y2 = 33 (golden 36); active ticks are 3px short. Deleting the constant throws. The active line's y2 attribute is 33 vs golden 36 (running state has lit ticks in both).",
      "checks": [{ "type": "attribute", "target": "y2" }],
      "where": [
        { "screen": "focus-timer", "state": "running", "viewport": "desktop" },
      ],
    },
    {
      "branch": "defect/cluster-2",
      "id": "c2-pause",
      "category": "interactive-states",
      "tier": "high",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"timer-countdown\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "setInterval is never cleared (cleanup dropped); pausing no longer stops the countdown. In the paused state golden freezes at the pause value (~24:58) while the defect keeps counting (~24:54). textContent differs.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "text-content" }],
      "where": [
        { "screen": "focus-timer", "state": "paused", "viewport": "desktop" },
      ],
    },

