      "category": "interactive-states",
      "tier": "high",
      "selector": "[data-testid=\"kanban-column-1\"] [data-testid=\"card-title\"]",
      "whatsWrong": "Add-card always targets swimlane.columns[0] instead of the clicked column; new cards land in the first column. After the add-card-col2 state clicks column-1's Add card, golden's column-1 gains a card (count 3) while the defect's stays at 2 (the card went to column-0). dom-count differs.",
      "checks": [{ "type": "dom-count" }],
